project_descr: The International Think Tank for Land Locked Developing Countries (ITT LLDCs) is aimed at providing support for strategic interventions to enhance the development prospects of all LLDCs.

outputs.output_descr: The International Think Tank  is aimed at providing support for strategic interventions to enhance the development prospects of all LLDCs. It is a platform for knowledge sharing, support for intra LLDC collaboration and other South-South engagement.
